track_notes:
Walked in the snow, so probably not optimal. Somebody can probably improve on this!

From good lay-by to east. Follow marker posts up permissive path to gate through wall. Skirt bottom of heather slope then grassy ramp (maybe - I just saw white stuff) to join quad track. Final climb to summit plateau.

Total time (including ops): 2hr 30m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Arenig Fach Linear from Llyn Celyn. Jul 2020.
